Web-Organize People Backgrounds for Chrome is a people photography themed browser extension.
Browser background images of high quality, professional photographs of real people, captured and brought to your screen!
Photography has the ability to capture real people and reflect the world we live in. It can provide a voice for individuals and groups within our communities, and above all, convey their unique stories. This extension is meant to deliver powerful, professionally captured moments of real people of the world in their environments straight to your browser as background images.
Install this extension to change your browser background.
Web-organize.co takes over a new tab extension and brings you Bing Search results to help you find what youâ€™re looking for, while enjoying the sights of real people of various cultures and professions
